content.Fri.000: Handling salty fish all day makes me real thirsty.
content.spring_9.001: Eh, I got a fish hook stuck in my thumb... the Doctor's gonna cut it out.
content.winter_17.000: Ah, nothin' like a hot beverage to wind down after a cold, dark day...
content.spring_9.000: I have a doctor's appointment today, so if you need to buy anything you'd better hurry.

content.Sat.000: Ah... Nothing's better than kicking back with a cold one after a relaxing day fishing.$h
content.winter_15.000: I can't get me a good night's sleep with that night market going on... eh, but that's okay. I'm flexible.
